# PDF to CBT Conversion Fix Plan

## Kya galat ho raha hai (Root Cause)

Main issue **Antigravity ke migration** mein hai — Supabase AI extraction ko Hugging Face backend se replace kiya gaya, lekin integration adhura chhoda gaya.

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    upload[User uploads PDF] --> pdfjs[pdfjs client-side text extract]
    pdfjs --> state[pdfText state filled]
    upload --> fileState[pdfFile state set]
    fileState --> extractBtn[Extract Questions click]
    extractBtn --> bug["requestBody = pdfBase64 only"]
    bug --> apiCall["API body: pdfText = ''"]
    apiCall --> hfError["HF returns: No text provided!"]
    state -.->|"IGNORED when pdfFile exists"| apiCall
```

### Bug #1 — Frontend empty text bhej raha hai (PRIMARY)

[`biro-test/src/pages/CreateTest.tsx`](https://github.com/rhin867/Biro-tests/blob/main/biro-test/src/pages/CreateTest.tsx) mein lines ~118–142:

- PDF upload par `requestBody = { pdfBase64, mimeType }` set hota hai
- API call sirf `{ pdfText: requestBody.pdfText || '' }` bhejti hai
- **`pdfText` state variable bilkul use nahi hoti** jab file upload ho
- Result: backend ko **hamesha empty string** milti hai → error: **"No text provided!"**

Yahi aapka exact error hai.

### Bug #2 — HF backend sirf text accept karta hai

Deployed [`app.py`](https://huggingface.co/spaces/rhin867/biro-tests-api/blob/main/app.py) par `/extract-questions` endpoint:

- Sirf `pdfText` field read karta hai
- `pdfBase64` ignore hota hai (frontend banata hai par bhejta nahi)
- Mathongo / StudyTesla PDFs aksar **scanned/image-based** hote hain — pdfjs se client-side text **empty ya bahut kam** aata hai
- Pehle Supabase function (`extract-questions/index.ts`) PDF ko **Gemini vision** se directly padh sakta tha — yeh capability HF backend mein missing hai

### Bug #3 — Antigravity ne kya galat kiya

| Pehle (working design) | Antigravity ne kya kiya | Result |
|---|---|---|
| Supabase → `pdfBase64` + Gemini OCR | HF backend → sirf `pdfText` | Scanned PDFs fail |
| Frontend → full payload bhejta tha | Frontend → empty `pdfText` bhejta hai | "No text" error |
| `userApiKey` Settings se pass hota tha (AnswerKeyInput) | CreateTest mein API key pass nahi | Backup path bhi broken |
| Local backend scratch mein PyMuPDF + regex tha | HF par alag simplified Gemini-only code | Inconsistent |

**Note:** GitHub `main` branch par URL sahi hai (`https://rhin867-biro-tests-api.hf.space`), lekin payload bug ab bhi hai. Local antigravity scratch ab bhi `localhost:7860` use karta hai — deploy nahi hua.

### Aapki 3 PDFs ke baare mein

- **Mathongo Question Paper** — mixed text + images; client text partial ho sakta hai
- **@StudyTesla.pdf** — aksar scanned/image-heavy; pdfjs text ≈ 0
- **Paid Analysis By Mathongo** — analysis/solutions PDF; question extraction ke liye alag format

In sab ke liye **Gemini ko PDF file directly dena zaroori** hai, sirf text nahi.

